# Cursor API usage

- Follow `.cursor/skills/prompt-before-api-ops/SKILL.md`
- **Never `git push`** without explicit user approval in the thread
- **Never** invoke Bugbot (`Task` bugbot, `review-bugbot`) unless the user asks
- Bugbot on PRs is manual-only — user comments `bugbot run`; do not push to "trigger review"
- Prefer local read/grep/shell over web search or GitHub MCP when sufficient
